194
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:55,359
You’re already at the peak of Indestructible Realm.

195
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:57,400
Wake up already.

196
00:13:06,160 --> 00:13:07,359
It’s already been seven days and seven nights...

197
00:13:07,920 --> 00:13:09,439
...since the battle with Qian.

198
00:13:11,440 --> 00:13:13,039
Seven days and seven nights?

199
00:13:13,640 --> 00:13:14,640
