208
00:14:15,920 --> 00:14:18,039
♪ No matter how turbulent tomorrow may be... ♪

209
00:14:18,040 --> 00:14:20,439
♪ ...even if it blinds my eyes, so what? ♪

210
00:14:22,520 --> 00:14:24,399
♪ I may not see the movements of fate... ♪

211
00:14:24,640 --> 00:14:27,039
♪ ...but my heart remains bright and clear. ♪

212
00:14:28,960 --> 00:14:30,999
♪ I hold my heart in both hands... ♪

213
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:31,759
♪ Ignoring her... ♪

214
00:14:31,800 --> 00:14:32,639
♪ Exchanging sun and moon... ♪

215
00:14:32,640 --> 00:14:34,239
♪ Whether black or white, I see with my own eyes. ♪

216
00:14:34,240 --> 00:14:34,879
♪ I see all living beings... ♪

217
00:14:34,880 --> 00:14:35,799
♪ ...and grant their wishes. ♪

218
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:37,439
♪ I know where you’re heading... ♪

219
00:14:37,520 --> 00:14:39,079
♪ Heading above the layered clouds... ♪

220
00:14:39,200 --> 00:14:40,439
♪ There is still a sky... ♪

221
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:41,199
♪ One world... ♪

222
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:46,159
♪ We shall go there together. ♪

223
00:14:47,760 --> 00:14:49,759
♪ Body without bright moon... ♪

224
00:14:49,840 --> 00:14:51,399
♪ With mountains and rivers by my side... ♪

225
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:54,519
♪ I don’t know why I am... ♪

226
00:14:54,760 --> 00:14:59,079
♪ I only want this moment of clarity. ♪

227
00:14:59,520 --> 00:15:00,799
♪ Having seen all the hardships... ♪

228
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:02,959
♪ With my own body... ♪

229
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:04,639
♪ I exchange for you by my side. ♪

230
00:15:06,280 --> 00:15:08,119
♪ No need to ask about the color of the sky... ♪

231
00:15:08,360 --> 00:15:09,879
♪ If there is no light... ♪

232
00:15:09,880 --> 00:15:12,799
♪ I will become the Milky Way. ♪

233
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:47,080
♪ To think I directly broke through... ♪

234
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:49,079
...from mid Pill Cloud Realm
all the way to peak Indestructible Realm.

235
00:15:51,560 --> 00:15:52,879
This devouring power of the Demon Venerable...

236
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:54,639
...really is shamelessly overpowered.

237
00:15:55,520 --> 00:15:57,599
Next, I just need to comprehend Saber Intent...

238
00:15:58,040 --> 00:15:59,439
...and I can advance to the Great Sun Realm.

239
00:16:00,560 --> 00:16:01,560
