243
00:16:07,480 --> 00:16:07,959
Just go home and ask!

244
00:16:07,960 --> 00:16:08,960
Just go home and ask!

245
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:10,000
Home...

246
00:16:10,440 --> 00:16:11,719
So chasing Qian...

247
00:16:12,440 --> 00:16:14,239
…actually brought me near Dongning Prefecture

248
00:16:15,560 --> 00:16:16,560
I wonder how everyone’s doing...

249
00:16:17,080 --> 00:16:18,080
