Qingping...

271
00:17:01,400 --> 00:17:02,879
You’re still going to the mines?

272
00:17:04,362 --> 00:17:05,417
this one,

273
00:17:06,080 --> 00:17:07,959
That newly arrived Jade Sun Palace Master...

274
00:17:08,200 --> 00:17:11,159
...said the Wang family would jointly manage the mines with us.

275
00:17:11,560 --> 00:17:14,079
But right now, only the Bai family still has a God Venerable.

276
00:17:15,120 --> 00:17:16,079
That mine...

277
00:17:16,720 --> 00:17:18,759
...is clearly being handed over to the Bai family.

278
00:17:19,360 --> 00:17:20,639
In East Dongning Prefecture...

279
00:17:21,120 --> 00:17:22,559
...the Bai family reigns supreme.

280
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:24,960
Clan Leader Grandpa...

281
00:17:25,600 --> 00:17:26,639
Meng Chuan...

282
00:17:27,120 --> 00:17:28,519
Still no news?

283
00:17:29,760 --> 00:17:31,239
The old master really is...

284
00:17:31,360 --> 00:17:32,959
He only told us not to worry...

285
00:17:33,280 --> 00:17:35,039
...but never said where the young master went.

286
00:17:35,680 --> 00:17:37,159
He didn’t make it to Primordial Mountain...

287
00:17:37,320 --> 00:17:39,039
...so why hasn’t he come home?

288
00:17:40,680 --> 00:17:41,680
Meng Chuan...

289
00:17:41,880 --> 00:17:42,959
Qingping.

290
00:17:43,440 --> 00:17:44,440
About the mine...

291
00:17:44,520 --> 00:17:45,999
...you’d better not go.

292
00:17:46,640 --> 00:17:49,999
But I heard people have been disappearing there lately...

293
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:51,319
...and they’re all young girls.

294
00:17:51,920 --> 00:17:53,199
I’m afraid the Bai family is behind it again.

295
00:17:58,320 --> 00:18:00,119
Then this old man will accompany you.

296
00:18:01,600 --> 00:18:02,759
No need, Grandpa Meng.

297
00:18:03,200 --> 00:18:03,879
The Meng family...

298
00:18:04,200 --> 00:18:05,479
...doesn’t need to get dragged into this mess.

299
00:18:07,200 --> 00:18:08,200
Sister Qingping...

300
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:15,639
Miss...

301
00:18:23,200 --> 00:18:23,999
Let’s go.

302
00:18:24,120 --> 00:18:25,120
Sister Wei...

303
00:18:34,680 --> 00:18:36,399
You all better remember this.

304
00:18:36,680 --> 00:18:38,199
You people from Dayue...

305
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:41,719
...should be grateful you can even beg for scraps here.

306
00:18:42,440 --> 00:18:44,279
Otherwise, if you’d stayed in Dayue...

307
00:18:44,400 --> 00:18:46,239
...you’d only have a path to death.

308
00:18:47,360 --> 00:18:49,959
So work your asses off and be thankful!

309
00:19:02,280 --> 00:19:03,359
People checked.

310
00:19:04,560 --> 00:19:05,799
Checked.

311
00:19:18,360 --> 00:19:19,479
Get on it.

312
00:19:52,120 --> 00:19:52,519
Here.

313
00:19:52,880 --> 00:19:53,880
If it’s not enough, come get more.

314
00:20:09,600 --> 00:20:10,199
Bai Zhu...

315
00:20:11,600 --> 00:20:12,879
Sister-in-law is here.

316
00:20:15,560 --> 00:20:17,239
What brings you here, sister-in-law?

317
00:20:17,680 --> 00:20:19,119
Looking for your little brother-in-law?

318
00:20:21,280 --> 00:20:21,799
Bai Zhu...

319
00:20:22,080 --> 00:20:24,479
I heard women have been disappearing at the mine lately.

320
00:20:24,880 --> 00:20:26,039
What exactly is going on?

321
00:20:32,200 --> 00:20:33,039
About that matter...

322
00:20:33,600 --> 00:20:35,279
I’ve already sent people to investigate.

323
00:20:47,840 --> 00:20:49,759
If sister-in-law is worried...

324
00:20:50,120 --> 00:20:52,519
...you can stay and investigate with me.

325
00:20:53,040 --> 00:20:55,479
Together.

326
00:20:56,000 --> 00:20:57,879
I know this has something to do with you.

327
00:20:58,440 --> 00:20:59,599
I will get to the bottom of it.

328
00:21:00,160 --> 00:21:01,239
Yun Qingping...

329
00:21:01,840 --> 00:21:04,039
Looks like you still don’t understand the situation.

330
00:21:04,520 --> 00:21:05,919
In East Dongning Prefecture now...

331
00:21:06,360 --> 00:21:08,279
I, Bai Zhu, call the shots.

332
00:21:09,120 --> 00:21:09,919
You, Bai Zhu...

333
00:21:10,240 --> 00:21:12,959
...are nothing but a bastard the Bai family God Venerable
sired outside.

334
00:21:13,480 --> 00:21:14,480
How do you know...

335
00:21:14,680 --> 00:21:15,919
...he doesn’t have a second one?

336
00:21:19,160 --> 00:21:19,759
Fine.

337
00:21:20,880 --> 00:21:23,399
You brought this death upon yourself.

338
00:21:31,080 --> 00:21:32,080
Miss...

339
00:21:32,280 --> 00:21:33,759
I told you not to come.

340
00:21:36,200 --> 00:21:36,639
She...

341
00:21:36,960 --> 00:21:38,279
...couldn’t just sit back and do nothing.

342
00:21:46,080 --> 00:21:46,559
What’s wrong?

343
00:21:46,800 --> 00:21:47,800
Why did we stop?

344
00:21:53,000 --> 00:21:54,000
Demons...

345
00:22:04,040 --> 00:22:05,040
Why...

346
00:22:05,080 --> 00:22:07,319
Why are there so many demons rushing over here?!

347
00:22:23,960 --> 00:22:24,960
Take the green bamboo.

348
00:22:29,440 --> 00:22:30,440
Root Technique.

349
00:22:30,680 --> 00:22:31,999
Rakshasa Eight Methods.

350
00:23:03,320 --> 00:23:04,320
Run into the mine!

351
00:23:11,920 --> 00:23:12,599
Open the gate!

352
00:23:12,800 --> 00:23:13,519
There are demons!

353
00:23:13,640 --> 00:23:14,559
Open the gate, quick!

354
00:23:19,400 --> 00:23:19,959
Bai Zhu!

355
00:23:20,120 --> 00:23:21,120
Open the gate!

356
00:23:22,240 --> 00:23:22,839
Brother Zhu...

357
00:23:23,160 --> 00:23:24,319
Are you really not opening it?

358
00:23:25,320 --> 00:23:26,320
What’s wrong?

359
00:23:26,480 --> 00:23:28,319
Can’t bear to lose your sister-in-law?

360
00:23:32,840 --> 00:23:34,359
Bai Zhu...

361
00:23:51,600 --> 00:23:53,119
With majestic divine might...

362
00:23:53,840 --> 00:23:55,239
...I command you by imperial decree!

363
00:24:00,880 --> 00:24:01,880
Thunder roars...

364
00:24:02,320 --> 00:24:03,320
Crush them!

365
00:24:18,560 --> 00:24:19,560
It’s a God Venerable!

366
00:24:21,360 --> 00:24:22,399
It’s him!

367
00:24:37,120 --> 00:24:38,439
God...

368
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:40,599
God Venerable...

369
00:25:02,280 --> 00:25:03,239
Why didn’t you open the gate just now?

370
00:25:03,263 --> 00:25:26,063
[By tempering the body and refining the blood, one awakens the latent power within the bloodline; through this force, a cultivator can comprehend the principles of heaven and earth, harmonize with the natural order, and gradually transcend mortal limits, ultimately manifesting a divine form and attaining a higher state of existence.]

371
00:25:26,088 --> 00:25:27,525
[“The blade slays evil; the brush paints all life.”]

372
00:25:27,549 --> 00:25:31,502
[The Divine Venerable Form is the core manifestation of a cultivator’s power, formed through the convergence of spirit, will, and comprehension of the Dao; although it appears as a single form, it contains countless variations depending on one’s path and insight, and only by fully understanding and stabilizing this form can one grasp true strength, refine it into reality, and ultimately inscribe one’s complete and perfect name within the realm of the divine.]

373
00:25:31,526 --> 00:25:32,906
[All demons must die.]

374
00:25:32,930 --> 00:25:35,858
[All forms of cultivation ultimately rely on the use of divine power, yet each individual’s foundation and strength differ, resulting in vast disparities; only by continuously refining and accumulating this power can one grow stronger, break through limitations, and fully manifest the Divine Venerable Form, transforming it from an intangible concept into a true and stable existence. The Divine Venerable Form originates within oneself and gradually transforms through cultivation; although the aura it emits may differ in strength and nature, it ultimately reflects the cultivator’s inner will and foundation, and only by continuously refining both body and spirit can one stabilize this power, allowing the Divine Venerable Form to take shape, evolve, and fully manifest its true potential.]

375
00:25:35,883 --> 00:25:37,398
[On the path I tread, nothing can stand in my way.]

376
00:25:37,422 --> 00:25:40,430
[Techniques are the methods through which a cultivator applies their power, integrating their understanding of heaven and earth with personal faith and experience; by mastering various forms of combat arts and skills, one can refine these techniques into distinct realms, each representing a different level of strength and application, ultimately allowing the cultivator to fully express their power through perfected technique.]

377
00:25:40,454 --> 00:25:41,818
[“I will guide all beings across—free from suffering.”]

378
00:25:41,842 --> 00:25:45,270
[The path of Divine Venerable cultivation is divided into five major realms: the Pill Condensation Realm, the Indestructible Realm, the Great Sun Realm, the Dark Star Realm, and the Boundless Realm; each realm represents a profound transformation in power and understanding, marking a cultivator’s steady ascent from mortal limits toward an unfathomable and limitless state of existence.]

379
00:25:45,295 --> 00:25:51,390
[Upon reaching the Pill Condensation Realm, a cultivator begins to give rise to their Divine Venerable Form, though it remains incomplete; advancing into the Indestructible Realm allows this form to stabilize and take shape, while entry into the Great Sun Realm marks the first true manifestation of its power; only after breaking through to the Dark Star Realm can one fully refine and control it, and upon stepping into the Boundless Realm, the Divine Venerable Form becomes complete and perfected, representing the pinnacle of cultivation.]

380
00:25:52,334 --> 00:25:57,123
[After reaching the Boundless Realm, a cultivator may condense a true Divine Venerable Form and step into the level of a titled Divine Venerable; at this stage, one gains deeper control over divine power and begins to establish their own Dao, while continued cultivation allows the form to evolve further, ultimately transcending all limitations, breaking free from the constraints of realms, and achieving a state where one’s Divine Venerable Form stands beyond all boundaries.]

381
00:25:57,147 --> 00:25:58,757
[“I am all beings—and all beings are me.”]

382
00:25:58,781 --> 00:26:03,424
[The Sword Sect follows the path of the sword as its core cultivation system, progressing through stages such as Sword Qi, Sword Light, Sword Intent, Sword Form, Sword Heart, and beyond, each representing a deeper mastery of swordsmanship and understanding; by refining these stages, one advances along a path of unmatched sharpness and precision, where a single sword can break all techniques, reaching a realm where the sword becomes absolute and invincible.]

383
00:26:03,448 --> 00:26:04,980
[“If I die, it will be on the path of slaying demons.”]

384
00:26:05,004 --> 00:27:58,438
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

